file_content.text: Torian. That trap ready?
No, and the traitor's on his way back.
Jicoln's still got one cache left, you think he's on to us?
He's early.
You think Jicoln's quitting the game?
Is he trying to run away?
He's just changing strategy.
You're winning; he's coming to fortify his stronghold.
Transmitting location. I'll do what I can. Hurry.
Don't let him get away. I'm heading to you now.
Pin him down.
I'll ambush him at his camp. Transmitting coordinates. Hurry there.
Ha! You're a real spitfire. If I were young again, I might take you as a bride, girl.
Ha! I haven't had this much fun in years, boy! I'm glad you didn't die too quickly after all!
Found the traitor's bolt-hole. Wreckage. Crashed ship. The Endar Spire.
I can head that direction.
You want me there?
No, keep him busy. I'm laying a trap.
Good work, Torian. I'll let you know when I've got Jicoln on the run.
Great job.
The game's already half over. You better pull it together and fast.
Took you long enough.
Keep the pressure on; I'll start laying a trap.
I'll call when everything's in position.
Finding one that quickly could have been dumb luck. Two, you're getting help. Let's slow you down.
Not bad... it's usually over by now. Let's see how far you get.
